{
  "stem": "7624.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Except my father was sick, and he was taken to the Mount Sinai-- no, Rothschild Hospital in Paris.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] From-- from Drancy, I didn't hear nothing no more for my parents or sister.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I found out my father's in-- in the hospital, and I got in touch with him somehow, again, through some connection-- underground connection.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And in 19-- late '43 or beginning '44, he was taken and sent to Drancy.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And from there, nothing no more, either.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They kept him, being sick, in the hospital for so-and-so many months.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And yes, so I went back to the organization.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I found them.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I said, give me my papers, and I would like to join the American army.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They asked me, please don't do it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Stay with us, because we have hundreds and thousands of children hidden all over, in convents, in French farmers, and so on.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we need somebody-- we need people who can get them out of there again.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That's what I did.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I stayed with the organization, and we looked for children.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And some children didn't want to come back to us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Some children were changed to be Catholic and didn't want to be Jewish again.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was a very difficult situation.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we-- the organization knew some places where they'd hidden--",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Same organization, OSE.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oeuvre de Secours aux Enfants.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They started to come back again who were underground, and they formed again the whole thing.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then they got a lot of help from the American Joint, money, advice, and so on.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Right after then, the Joint was very powerful, and they helped us tremendously.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Also, the Baron of Rothschild left us a lot of money for those children's' homes.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Clothes and--",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
